  "remarks": "Passport no.: Georgian passport number 09AL14455 expires on 26 Jun. 2019 National identification no.: Georgian national identification number 08001007864. As of mid-2014, Syria-based senior military commander and shura council member of Islamic State in Iraq and the Levant, listed as Al-Qaida in Iraq (AQI) (QE.J.115.04). Led approximately 1,000 foreign fighters for ISIL and committed a number of attacks in northern Syria. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 2368 (2017) was concluded on 24 November 2020.; Listing: Listed on 23 Jan. 2015 (amended on 24 Nov. 2020)",
